We need to complete the proof of the Marcinkiewicz-Zygmund inequality for symmetric random variables. The inequality states that if $X_1, \ldots, X_n$ are independent symmetric random variables in some inner product space, then $\|X_1 + \cdots + X_n\|_p \leq C_p \cdot \| \|X_1\|^2 + \cdots + \|X_n\|^2\|^{p/2}$ for $p \geq 2$.

